# Never upload local env files via `vercel deploy` (CLI).
# The CLI bundles project files into the deployment; a local .env would
# bake dev-only secrets (e.g. a local MCP_AUTH_TOKEN) into the lambda's
# process.env and SHADOW the real Vercel-managed env vars + the bootstrap
# KV token. Real values come from the Vercel project env + Upstash KV.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
